title: Canon EOS Digital Solution Disk ver 17.1 (Windows)
description:
This is the Windows application disc that comes with Canon EOS Rebel XSi/450D cameras, which for some reason is not available through the Canon website yet.  I know I always lose my discs, so here is a backup for those who do the same (and probably me in a few months)

Contains:
Digital Photo Professional 3.3
ZoomBrowserEX 6.1
EOS Utility 2.3
PhotoStitch 3.1
Drivers
Ogiginal Data Security Tools 1.3
Picture Style Editor 1.2
WFT Utility 3.2
